# 📌 tasks/audit.yml

```yaml
- name: Write audit log
  copy:
    dest: "{{ audit_file }}"
    content: |
      ==========================================
      MSTR Plugin Deployment Audit
      ==========================================
      Timestamp: {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}
      Namespace: {{ namespace }}
      Pods: {{ final_pods }}
      Plugins: {{ active_plugins }}
      Backup: {{ backup_local_dir }}
      UI Status: {{ ui_health.rc == 0 | ternary('SUCCESS','FAILED') }}
```

